                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Frequency</b> once per day; <b>Effect</b> The ether spider flings a gout of stored webs in a 30-foot cone. These webs can pass between the Material Plane and the Ethereal Plane. Each creature in the area is <a aonid=\"24\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">immobilized</a>, as ethereal web trap, unless it succeeds at a DC 22 Reflex save.",
